          {
            "turoyo": "Meqəm ṭurone kətwa, u ʕamo d-əmmat lo masxewa d-qoṭaʕwa. 2019_13_01_Malfono_İshaq",
            "translations": [],
            "references": []
          },
          {
            "turoyo": "U Ḥabib lo masxele d-oxal u malayḏe w maṯ kafino. (İlyas p.c) Habib did not dare to spend his property and died of hunger.",
            "translations": [],
            "references": []
          }
        ],
        "Infectum": [
          {
            "turoyo": "İ žabaše lә gmasxeno d towarna.",
