              "İlyas p.c"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "Infectum-wa": [
          {
            "turoyo": "kət-way-le qarno maḥat-way-la ʕal-dukṯe d-u=ǧroḥo d-i=mus-ayo w-moyaṣ-wa b-feme me-qarʕe d-u=qarno w-bəṯṯər b-ʕarše soxar-wa u=naqwo d-kətyo eba me-lalʕal b-u=šamʕo",
            "translations": [
              "‘He (doctor, m.) had a horn. He put it on the place of the injury from the razor, sucked the top of the horn and then with his teeth he shut the upper opening (of the horn) using wax’ LuF 294/29;"
            ],
            "references": []
          }
        ],
        "Imperative": [
          {
            "turoyo": "sxar i=dukano",
            "translations": [
              "mach deinen Laden zu"
            ],
            "references": [
              "MM 141"
            ]
          },
          {
            "turoyo": "sxaru at=tarʕe w-zano l-u=bayto!",
            "translations": [
              "‘Close the gates and let’s go home!’; 43/11"
            ],
            "references": []
          }
        ],
        "Participle_Passive": [
          {
            "turoyo": "kila daməxto, nafas kiba w-ʕayna sxire, lu=k-qudro d-məžġolo ‘",
            "translations": [
              "Sie schläft, sie hat noch Lebensodem in sich, aber ihre Augen sind geschlossen und sie kann nicht sprechen"
            ],
            "references": [
              "24/71"
